1 shot = 2 floz
1 dash = 1/32 floz
1 splash = 4 dash

Flavor Mix:
  MUDDLE until "paste"
    MIX
      1 tsp Sugar
      1 splash Water
      2 dash Angostura Bitters
    1 Maraschino Cherry
    1 Orange Wedge

Old Fashioned:
  STIR in "old-fashioned glass"
    Ice Cubes
    POUR
      1 shot Bourbon
      Flavor Mix
